# lerobot_policy_latent_smolvla

Standalone LeRobot policy plugin for a latent-supervised SmolVLA variant.

This package starts from the upstream SmolVLA policy and adds:

- an auxiliary latent head
- dataset-key-based latent targets
- masked action and latent loss reduction for mixed-supervision batches

It is intentionally lighter than the HLRP shared-core policy and does not perform
online LAM inference.
